flowchart TD
    A[Start Analysis] --> B{Input valid?}
    B -- no --> E1[Exit with user-facing error]
    B -- yes --> C{Resources init ok?}
    C -- no --> E2[RuntimeError from pipeline init]
    C -- yes --> D{Parse/chunk/embed/analyze success?}
    D -- no --> E3[Pipeline failure + logged exception]
    D -- yes --> F[Generate outputs + audit]
    F --> G[Success summary]
